但係個樓豬同幾個活躍巴打都反張寶欣<br />\n一留言十卜即刻被人當五毛咁攻擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為求和平我先決條定咁樣分開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你唔洗同我解釋喎 其實我都唔LIKE張寶欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只不過我覺得某條友係咁吹奏大口大鼻怪好撚煩</blockquote><br />\n我唔介意佢地負皮 我都知張小姐受歡迎程度不高 但係佢地嘅舉動根本挑起罵戰 所以先唔歡迎佢地留言<br />\nbtw 其實Boanne冇獎甚至冇入10強我都會支持佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"217890ddf005333e3b684188b55022c4ebf8ad0a","tid":495954,"uid":32719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:02:22.000Z","msg":"又係你丫 ig張相仲唔轉 又自爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e2ba6f837443aa77b16c2a4966e6b13214f25b7","tid":495954,"uid":32719,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:04:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/200424_a462d3eb7b886ddea4acaa9787e20acd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F200424_a462d3eb7b886ddea4acaa9787e20acd.jpg&h=3b93ab00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/200425_bf4fa2f0b6ce80b7ca03e8c4d84fba5e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F200425_bf4fa2f0b6ce80b7ca03e8c4d84fba5e.jpg&h=f2a2cd30&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/13/200425_1a0a73e4556cf6ed0c755372927b6e3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F13%2F200425_1a0a73e4556cf6ed0c755372927b6e3a.jpg&h=ffd91319&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一定幫你 改左名就得？"},{"pid":"0d4c7155071e019ded25ebc5a7a9662d3ef120d8","tid":495954,"uid":32719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T12:05:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"46714e268b875359361d7abc95e25929072f525c","ti