ass=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢個腦裝屎架？冇佢家姐佢而加會有人識？ 臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfa4928ab0d32e49cf7d34ab2107bfe8919417df","tid":495954,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:23:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臭閪張寶欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靜係識借家姐關係上位，仲攞撚埋人地個獎，比賽靜係得笑笑笑<br />\n歡樂滿東華要佢rap，有得背都可以甩beat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢個腦裝屎架？冇佢家姐佢而加會有人識？ 臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n最後果句我認同嘅<br />\n我都因為張寶兒先留意到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過bbc獎是咪佢拎我冇在意到，純粹覺得佢好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果佢願意交番個獎出黎比金美黎我亦冇任何意見 (不過金美黎自己都已經棄簽大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)"},{"pid":"04fd5df66d5609412cb631c82741d9a055430113","tid":495954,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-13T15:24:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臭閪張寶欣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 靜係識借家姐關係上位，仲攞撚埋人地個獎，比賽靜係得笑笑笑<br />\n歡樂滿東華要佢rap，有得背都可以甩beat<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢個腦裝屎架？冇佢家姐佢而加會有人識？ 臭雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為隔離po講張寶欣講到鬧交我先咁做者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}